Insanely proud of my staff. Their own time, their own initiative, organized a food drive with Share The Warmth.

The grand total? 640 cans/food items.
I will shout this from the rooftops until the end of time.
Wonderful time last night with my team at our Holiday party. Much fun was had, even more food and drink consumed and I even got to make a speech. So a win-win all around.
The Friday before the Holiday break...
The best, and only, advice I can give at the end of the year...
Anyone else's end of the year be like-
If you ain't laughing at yourself while dancing, you ain't dancing right.
This is why I don't keep a tidy house.
Not us cutting some corners during winter break...
That feeling, when you're still in the studio, on December 29th...
For 2023, let's all go a little easier on ourselves, yes?
Forget the New Year's Eve Parties. This is what we're doing tonight.  We're bloopin'!
Starting 2023 like-
Ending the holiday season with an epiphany of sorts, and yet, the animations, they need to be animated.
Somewhere, out in the great expanse of the universe, there exists an animation studio with a staff that knows how to properly clean dishes. But it is not here.
I know what you're thinking. How did you never make the connection before now?
Little know fact, but the MLP set is right next to ours. We share craft services.
DRAGON FACT 10293: We're a lot better at animating than we are at small talk.
You don't tell us how to live.
This should not have passed QA....

Mondays are hard, okay?
